item.title: Meetup - Thursday 6th December 2018 at The ODI Node in Leeds
item.description: We're going to see the new year out in style at The ODI Node in Leeds on Thursday 6th December 2018: 6:45 - 7:15 : Doors open, have a chat, make some new devops friends 7:15 - 7:25 : Group updates/news/announcements 7:25 - 8:05 : DevTest Microsoft stack environments. 8:05 - 8:20 : Intermission 8:20 - 9:00 : Terraform 0.12 guided tour Our first speaker is Sam Williams, Sam has been in the IT industry for nearly 15 years.
